  "purpose": "Companion REFERENCE cut to 'Kokoro: Free Voices (With Names)' — for people who want to hear the full 28 English voices before casting. Bear's ElevenLabs clone introduces (B00, the only paid audio); then all 28 voices speak in group order (11 af, 9 am, 4 bf, 4 bm), each stating name, origin, and the pack's own grade, then the SAME closing line ('The machine brings the hands — you bring the taste.') so listeners compare voices, not scripts. Heart (the pack's only A) closes. One props-driven Remotion card (KokoroRosterCard) renders every roster beat — name, code, group, grade chip, index. Rides OUTSIDE the chapter order (no chapter_number) as a reference; descriptions cross-link both ways with the short film. Grades verified against hexgrad/Kokoro-82M VOICES.md 2026-07-13; FACTCHECK re-verifies against --list-voices at build.",
